## Summary
This documentation page explains how to track revenue events in Amplitude, covering revenue properties, tracking methods for both in-app and external purchases, and revenue verification. It details the required properties ($revenue or $price/$quantity), explains the three types of revenue events (verified/unverified), and discusses how to enable receipt validation for iOS and Android purchases.

